  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd\u2019\u2019 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't act like 'Mr Bean': Vijitha",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Claiming that he came to power to solve the problems of the country, Ranil should inform the people how to solve the problems of the people as a responsible Prime Minister. Instead, Vijitha Herat, a member of the People's Liberation Front, told the Prime Minister that he should not act like Mr. Bean.",
        "Yesterday (6) during the Prime Minister's Question Time in Parliament Vijitha Herath MP. He raised questions about the problems faced by the people of the country. Also, the Ministers informed this House that the fuel ship will arrive on the 23rd.",
        "But now there is no hope for the arrival of the ship. He therefore asked what action the government would take against the ministers who had misled Parliament.",
        "The Prime Minister replied to this, only answer whether you are taking responsibility for the government or not. Your leader Anurakumara Dissanayake said that he will not take responsibility. You said you will take responsibility. Tell me one of these two.",
        "Commenting on the occasion, Vijitha Herath MP, do not act like Mr. Bean and as a responsible Prime Minister tell me the steps taken to solve the problems of the people. If you are acting like Mr. Bean, come and sit in opposition. You are currently the responsible Prime Minister of the country. So answer the questions asked about the issues related to people's lives, he said."
      ],
